metadata.name: Cybernetic Rapture
metadata.description:
Past meets present with LeiMai LeMaow's genesis piece. A cyborg girl from the future named Netty gazes at Gary, a character from the past, nod to old skool rave.

A physical piece accompanies this NFT, another tale of past meets present. The physical piece is painted in a traditional manner and embellished with 12ct Italian white gold and 23ct gold.
